Go ahead.

01:02:53.433 --> 01:02:57.100
The -- but you guys can -- feel
free to stand together if you

01:02:57.100 --> 01:02:59.233
want, but -- (laughter) -- I'm
only going to take a question

01:02:59.233 --> 01:03:00.166
from one of you.

01:03:00.166 --> 01:03:00.800
(laughter)

01:03:00.800 --> 01:03:01.533
What's your name?

01:03:01.533 --> 01:03:04.100
Audience Member: 
