01:03:05.066 --> 01:03:08.567
(applause)

01:03:08.567 --> 01:03:09.066
Thank you.

01:03:09.066 --> 01:03:11.500
President Obama,
I met you in 2006.

01:03:11.500 --> 01:03:14.333
I was working for the embassy.

01:03:14.333 --> 01:03:14.934
The President: 
Excellent.

01:03:14.934 --> 01:03:15.800
Audience Member: 
